    <formulas>
        <name>AccountName</name>
        <dataType>String</dataType>
        <expression>IF(
  $Record.SalesOrder__r.Account__r.IsPersonAccount,
  $Record.SalesOrder__r.Account__r.FirstName &amp; &quot; &quot; &amp; $Record.SalesOrder__r.Account__r.LastName,
  $Record.SalesOrder__r.Account__r.Name
)</expression>
    </formulas>
    <formulas>
        <name>InvoiceARBody</name>
        <dataType>String</dataType>
        <expression>&apos;تم فوترة الدفعة الخاصة بك للوحدة &apos; + {!$Record.SalesOrder__r.UnitNumber__c} + &apos; على &apos; + TEXT({!$Record.TypeOfCharge__c}) + IF(ISBLANK(TEXT({!$Record.SubType__c})), &apos;&apos;, &apos; - &apos; + TEXT({!$Record.SubType__c})) + &apos; بمبلغ &apos; + TEXT({!$Record.InvoicedAmount__c}) + &apos; &apos; + TEXT({!$Record.CurrencyIsoCode}) + &apos;.يرجى استكمال المبلغ المستحق.&apos;</expression>
    </formulas>
    <formulas>
        <name>InvoiceARTitle</name>
        <dataType>String</dataType>
        <expression>&apos;فوترة المبلغ الخاص بالوحدة &apos; + {!$Record.SalesOrder__r.UnitNumber__c} + &apos; ل &apos; + TEXT({!$Record.TypeOfCharge__c}) + IF(ISBLANK(TEXT({!$Record.SubType__c})), &apos;&apos;, &apos; - &apos; + TEXT({!$Record.SubType__c}))</expression>
    </formulas>
    <formulas>
        <name>InvoiceBody</name>
        <dataType>String</dataType>
        <expression>&apos;Your payment for  &apos; + {!$Record.SalesOrder__r.UnitNumber__c} + &apos; related to &apos; + TEXT({!$Record.TypeOfCharge__c}) + IF(ISBLANK(TEXT({!$Record.SubType__c})), &apos;&apos;, &apos; - &apos; + TEXT({!$Record.SubType__c})) + &apos; charges totaling &apos; + TEXT({!$Record.InvoicedAmount__c}) + &apos; &apos; + TEXT({!$Record.CurrencyIsoCode}) + &apos; has been billed. Please proceed with the necessary arrangements&apos;</expression>
    </formulas>
    <formulas>
        <name>InvoiceTitle</name>
        <dataType>String</dataType>
        <expression>&apos;Payment is billed for &apos; + {!$Record.SalesOrder__r.UnitNumber__c} + &apos; for &apos; + TEXT({!$Record.TypeOfCharge__c}) + IF(ISBLANK(TEXT({!$Record.SubType__c})), &apos;&apos;, &apos; - &apos; + TEXT({!$Record.SubType__c}))</expression>
    </formulas>
    <formulas>
        <name>ReminderARBody</name>
        <dataType>String</dataType>
        <expression>&apos;نود تذكيركم بأن الدفعة الخاصة بك للوحدة &apos; + {!$Record.SalesOrder__r.UnitNumber__c} + &apos; على &apos; + TEXT({!$Record.TypeOfCharge__c}) + IF(ISBLANK(TEXT({!$Record.SubType__c})), &apos;&apos;, &apos; - &apos; + TEXT({!$Record.SubType__c})) + &apos; بمبلغ &apos; + TEXT({!$Record.OutstandingAmount__c}) + &apos; &apos; + TEXT({!$Record.CurrencyIsoCode}) + &apos; لا تزال مستحقة. يرجى اتمام عملية الدفع.&apos;</expression>
    </formulas>
    <formulas>
        <name>ReminderARTitle</name>
        <dataType>String</dataType>
        <expression>&apos;اشعار بالدفع على &apos; + {!$Record.SalesOrder__r.UnitNumber__c} + &apos; ل &apos; + TEXT({!$Record.TypeOfCharge__c}) + IF(ISBLANK(TEXT({!$Record.SubType__c})), &apos;&apos;, &apos; - &apos; + TEXT({!$Record.SubType__c}))</expression>
    </formulas>
    <formulas>
        <name>ReminderBody</name>
        <dataType>String</dataType>
        <expression>&apos;We would like to remind you that your &apos; + TEXT({!$Record.TypeOfCharge__c}) + IF(ISBLANK(TEXT({!$Record.SubType__c})), &apos;&apos;, &apos; - &apos; + TEXT({!$Record.SubType__c})) + &apos; charges for &apos; + {!$Record.SalesOrder__r.UnitNumber__c} + &apos; remain outstanding. The total amount due is &apos; + TEXT({!$Record.OutstandingAmount__c}) + &apos; &apos; + TEXT({!$Record.CurrencyIsoCode}) + &apos;.&apos;</expression>
    </formulas>
    <formulas>
        <name>ReminderTitle</name>
